Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Conan Episode 808 \N"The Kamaitachi Inn (Part 1)"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:03.48,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking about a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:03.48,DCNote,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:08.62,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you got any bloodcurdling-ly \Ninteresting cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:10.48,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:17.52,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,There is something, but I haven't \Nfound any information yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:22.70,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't get Hattori caught up in \Ninvestigating Rum of the Black Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.34,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.02,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.29,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:31.08,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you haven't lost your edge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:34.02,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,since confessing your feelings\Nto the detective agency girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:38.08,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You know, your instincts \Nfor sniffing out cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.97,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Or your antenna, you could call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:42.43,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:46.22,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If I did, I wouldn't be calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.84,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No, you must have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:49.61,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:53.08,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And you're bringing it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:53.99,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:55.99,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Untitled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.99,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Playing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:56.88,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask you the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.88,0:01:01.57,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're\Ndoing to my Kazuha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:07.77,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,With the same feelings we've \Nalways held still in our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:10.01,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,we fly powerfully into our twentieth year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:13.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Right in front of mine and Hattori's eyes,\Nstabbings happen one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.13,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth with the \Nbody of a child and the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:19.22,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:07.01,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(399,1)}The Kamaitachi Inn\N(Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.46,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"The Kamaitachi Inn, Part One!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.50,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:12.88,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,You can really taste the \Nginger in this kuzuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:14.99,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,It warms you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.00,DCMain,KAZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:20.01,DCMain,KAZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,It said in an article that this \Ninn's kuzuyu is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.25,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:25.13,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The kuzuyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.67,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,It's suppose to be good for hangovers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:32.10,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I meant surely you didn't invite \Nthe great detective Mori Kogoro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:36.65,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,to an inn deep in the mountains of \NNagano just to eat this slimy stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.65,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:43.36,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a case, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.12,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:48.34,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,First, look at this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:49.95,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,A person. No, an animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.94,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:58.55,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely at what it's got on its back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.55,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,A sickle. And speaking of \Nanimals that have sickles,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:07.70,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,there's a demon that rides in on whirlwinds \Nand cuts people clean in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.97,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The kamaitachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.40,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:12.60,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kamaitachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:17.98,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought kamaitachi \Nhave sickles for fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.24,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a person carrying a sickle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:23.62,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Look at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.53,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The water's spraying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:31.01,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The background is the outdoor \Nbath here at this inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:36.04,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,but this is a photo taken from the same \Nangle by the writer who published the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:37.85,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Compare them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:41.55,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,He's clearly walking on \Nthe surface of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.67,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:49.93,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he lined up a couple \Ntransparent platforms in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:55.95,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The water here is clouded\Nlike the Shirahone Hot Spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:58.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,which makes all kinds of tricks possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.82,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't do anything to the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:05.54,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,And the photo was taken with analog \Nfilm, which is difficult to edit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:09.34,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,I even had an expert look at it, \Nso it's definitely the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:12.70,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the writer who took this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:17.33,Daigo,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Nakama Daigo (35)\NWriter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:17.33,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah. I'm Nakama Daigo, a \Nwriter for IZUNA magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:22.16,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here today to take a picture \Nof the kamaitachi myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.37,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.73,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten really cold lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.50,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,What does the cold have \Nto do with kamaitachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:33.67,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,The kamaitachi legend is \Npopular in snowy regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:40.69,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,So if it snows tonight, he might \Ncome riding in on the snow and wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:42.85,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.78,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:45.43,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:50.99,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he does appear, we can beat \Nhim up with my aikido and your karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.40,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're talking about a creature armed \Nwith a sickle that flies around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.93,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,He'd get us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:57.35,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:01.35,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The kamaitachi never existed \Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:08.47,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,You're here because you received so many \Ncomplaints about your phony photo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:14.68,Midori,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Koyanagi Midori (26)\NWriter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:15.35,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Besides, that photo was mixed in \Nwith a bunch of voyeuristic photos
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:19.02,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,of the outdoor bath printed in another \None of your publisher's magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:22.03,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dubious, I could laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:24.59,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:31.39,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I write for a rival magazine, so I came\Nto write an article on your hack writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.05,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I won't let you \Nstage anything, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:37.36,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,to make this non-existent \Nkamaitachi seem like it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.45,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,He does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:43.59,Kohei,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Ono Kohei (7)\NLandlady's Son
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:43.59,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I saw the kamaitachi running \Nacross the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:45.53,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:50.98,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I tried to chase him, \Nbut I can't walk on water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:53.97,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I almost drowned\Nbecause I couldn't move,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.39,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,like a spell was cast on me or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.02,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up, I was lying down \Nin the hallway, soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.52,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.52,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kohei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.07,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.73,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:09.07,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Did you already finish decorating the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:12.99,Takami,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Ono Takami (34)\NInn Landlady
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:12.99,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We're celebrating your birthday \Ntomorrow with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:15.55,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm about to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.08,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Then go and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.33,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.41,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, your hands are badly chapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:24.06,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Takami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:29.09,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've been working more since \Nmy husband passed away last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.24,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.72,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:35.93,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we were classmates in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:39.08,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for publishing that \Nweird photo in the magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:40.70,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it hasn't caused you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:43.73,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No. Thanks to the photo, we've \Nbeen getting more guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:49.23,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Though because of the kamaitachi, fewer \Npeople have been using the outdoor bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:53.99,Bonzo,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Ono Bonzo (72)\NLadylady's Father-in-law
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.62,DCMain,BONZO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kamaitachi, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.99,DCMain,BONZO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This couldn't be worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:56.11,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:08:01.20,DCMain,BONZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. That monster will only bring \Nin more customers for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.00,DCMain,BONZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a fundamental solution \Nto our money problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:10.01,DCMain,BONZO,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way to \Nbring in more customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.63,DCMain,BONZO,0000,0000,0000,,Right, landlady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:15.31,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you I'm not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:21.33,DCMain,BONZO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, once the fuss dies down and you \Ncan't keep the business open anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.19,DCMain,BONZO,0000,0000,0000,,you'll change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:29.97,DCMain,BONZO,0000,0000,0000,,Though it'd be a different story if that \Nkamaitachi actually killed someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nyotaimori?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:41.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,He wants you to get naked so customers \Ncan eat sashimi off your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:44.46,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He said it'd double \Nthe number of guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.80,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I've only ever seen that \Nin dirty historical dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.60,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If it got out, you'd be charged \Nwith public indecency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.72,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's only joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:09:01.17,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,When we got married, my family and theirs \Nmerged our inns, and business was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.80,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But since my husband died,\Na lot of regulars stopped coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.98,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,and it's true that we're in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:11.11,DCMain,NAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But, Takami, you can't do a nyotaimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.19,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sell something, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.24,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Like antique pots or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.01,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:21.67,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,there is a large sickle in the \Nstorehouse that a famous swordsmith
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:24.82,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,modeled after a foreign grass sickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:27.37,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be worth good money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.38,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,About how big is that sickle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.57,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The blade is 60 centimeters long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:37.63,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The handle is as long as I am tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:41.18,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:44.39,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The sickle the kamaitachi \Nwas carrying in the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:47.23,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the storehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.97,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Next to the outdoor bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:50.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Show us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.43,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.38,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Pretty interesting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.21,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Then give me the audio file.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.36,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:06.83,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.76,DCMain,KAZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Heiji, we'll leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:09.70,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:10.56,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:16.21,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It should be around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.53,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:25.29,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,This storehouse is covered in dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:28.96,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You'll start a fire if you smoke in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.85,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.44,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we split up and help you look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.26,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.99,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.25,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.60,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:44.62,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.41,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.12,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:52.67,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,But snow means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.52,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,The kamaitachi is coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:03.25,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you were \Ngoing to wait outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.06,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this it, Takami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:10.21,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's it. This is the sickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.54,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is antique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.06,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Looks valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:17.69,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My late husband said it \Nwas worth 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:19.99,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:21.74,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,The light bulb broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:24.03,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.08,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:26.69,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:27.54,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:30.38,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened, \Nbut something cut my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.00,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And the back of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.21,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.16,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You're both bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.09,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,That was the lady writer's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.50,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:44.44,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:45.97,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.02,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that cut....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:55.32,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:57.94,DCItalic,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,The kamaitachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.03,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:08.33,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call the cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:12.12,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they said they'd be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:16.67,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if they'll believe you \Nwere assaulted by a kamaitachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:22.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, they've got three people \Nright here who were cut by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.76,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.45,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're in Nagoya, the \NNagano police will be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:30.10,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Inspector Yamato Kansuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.80,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:39.07,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,That super smart one-eyed inspector \Nwill arrest the kamaitachi in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:39.98,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.79,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,One-eyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.51,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:49.12,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Haibara mentioned the number two of the \NBlack Organization's special trait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:53.87,DCItalic,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,While I was in the organization, \NI heard all kinds of descriptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.25,DCItalic,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,A large brawny man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:58.88,DCItalic,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,An effeminate man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.01,DCItalic,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,An old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.52,DCItalic,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,He injured an eye in some kind of accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:08.01,DCItalic,HAIBARA,0000,0000,0000,,Either his right or left \Neye is an artificial eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:12.54,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Yamato is one-eyed and a big guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:15.61,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,His hair is long enough that he ties it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:20.40,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,And since he walks with a cane, \Nhe might look old from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:23.83,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Inspector Yamato \Ncouldn't possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.99,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The police are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.78,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:38.79,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Gunma Police Inspector\NYamamura has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:43.32,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we in Nagano?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:46.63,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,We're just on the border of Gunma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:49.05,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,This is my jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:53.22,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Yamato couldn't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:56.06,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd get to see Yui-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.66,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.90,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:04.47,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,The flaming dog case, the kappa case,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.03,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,and even the vampire case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:11.53,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I helped solve all those \Ncases from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:18.41,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,If the culprit is a kamaitachi, then of course\Nthey'll send me, Demon Hunter Yamamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.41,DCNote,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Hunter Yamamura
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:25.50,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Though in our scientific age of orbital \Nelevators that will take you to space,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.42,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way kamaitachi exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:31.43,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've heard that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:36.97,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Now show me to the storehouse where \Nyou were assaulted by the kamaitachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.85,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm sure it's some kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.86,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is infuriating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:49.11,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You came here to \Nlook for an antique sickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:52.90,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Then this light bulb suddenly \Nexploded, and in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:56.40,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,someone cut the back of \NMori-san's right hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:59.00,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,the Osaka accented kid's left arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:06.08,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,and the left cheek of the \Nwriter Koyanagi Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:06.84,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:11.24,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone have anything sharp at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:15.35,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was holding the antique sickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:19.48,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,The light bulb shattered just \Nas I found it and picked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:26.36,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Then perhaps you swung that \Nsickle around in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:27.85,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:31.50,DCMain,HEIIJI,0000,0000,0000,,If he swung that around, we would've \Nbeen cut way worse than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:36.92,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we check the sickle for blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:39.00,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I will, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:45.33,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Was there someone standing near the \Nlight bulb who could have broken it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.50,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe, but I didn't see anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.10,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,There was nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:55.76,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,We were standing in the doorway then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:16:01.14,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Just before the light bulb broke, \Neveryone was looking at the sickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.41,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the only light bulb?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:06.02,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.19,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's usually another by the entrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:12.24,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,but it wouldn't turn on when we \Nentered the storehouse today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:16.03,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this storehouse \Ndoesn't have a lock, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:20.93,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No. The door is old and rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:26.54,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,All we ever stored in this storehouse \Nwe planned to demolish was rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:30.14,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But you said the sickle \Nwas worth 10 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:33.44,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what my late husband said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:37.05,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My father-in-law thinks \Nit's just a piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:40.92,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A few days ago, a burglar broke \Ninto the storehouse again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.66,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to replace the \Ndoor and put a lock on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:49.32,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,but my father-in-law said we didn't \Nneed to since we're in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.87,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What did the burglar take?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:56.69,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing we couldn't live without.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:57.70,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.20,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the sickle in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:05.14,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,It looks exactly like something an ancient \Ndemon would use, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:08.60,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I, Demon Hunter Yamamura,\Nwill catch him immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.71,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,so you needn't be worried sick-le.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:12.74,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A pun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.72,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,What? The kamaitachi appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.94,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky. I wanted to see him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.23,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:24.10,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Some people were hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:30.91,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,When I nearly drowned in the hot spring, \NI was probably saved by the kamaitachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:33.16,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.99,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you finish decorating the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.92,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:41.87,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it like Dad did by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:45.95,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm too busy to help you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:49.04,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Want us to help you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.13,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the decorating to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:52.46,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:54.49,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.67,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:56.88,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:57.77,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.56,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.53,DCMain,KOHEI,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.29,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Eight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:09.65,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you really celebrated \Nyour son's birthday every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.56,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the photos on the inn's homepage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:15.23,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my husband loved big events.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.48,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,During a party for my husband's \Nsurvival game friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:22.30,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,they got water everywhere while \Nshooting each other with water guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:23.42,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It was a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.03,DCMain,NAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.24,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.75,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:32.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure someone \Ndid it in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:37.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,But if nobody was carrying anything sharp...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.09,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,The weapon was probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.34,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,...a fragment of the shattered light bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:45.27,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know how \Nthey broke the light bulb,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:51.35,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,but they definitely used a piece of a \Ndifferent light bulb that they had all along, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:56.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. By throwing it on the \Nfloor after cutting everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.53,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,they could make it look like one of \Nthe pieces that was broken off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:08.00,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,After examining the sickle for \Nblood, the results determined
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.00,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,that there was none.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:14.13,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:18.57,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,And? Did you examine the shards of the\Nlight bulb scattered on the floor, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:21.51,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, though there was \Nnothing unusual about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:24.36,DCMain,COONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What? There wasn't blood on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:26.81,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,You really did examine them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.24,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:32.35,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,We gathered up all the pieces and \Nreassembled them into their original shape,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.98,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,but there wasn't any blood anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.72,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:38.23,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Then how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:44.74,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,The only unusual things we found were \Ncigarette butts and a piece of chewed gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:54.01,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,I believe an old light bulb simply shattered \Nand happened to hit the three of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:57.85,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should've felt \Npain the instant it broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.86,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,But there was a delay between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:06.10,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the girls' voices!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.97,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear that sound before they screamed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.67,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,That sounded like something \Nbreaking and bursting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.19,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:16.12,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.35,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The lamp suddenly broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:22.36,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,And then the balloons we put up popped.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.74,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This inn must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.12,DCMain,KAZUHA,0000,0000,0000,,...haunted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:31.11,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:32.99,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:35.12,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did the kamaitachi get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.54,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:40.34,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,At this hour, probably in the annex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:45.09,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait. Isn't there a faster way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.64,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The fastest way is through the outdoor bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.75,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. There's still water in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.02,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not time to clean yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:02.32,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Is that building on the other \Nside of the fence the annex?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.30,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.22,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:07.66,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Does that gate look slightly open to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:10.02,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the kamaitachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:14.13,DCMain,NAKAMA,0000,0000,0000,,The kamaitachi rode the \Nwind across the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.29,DCMain,KOYANAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:21.75,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like there are any \Ntransparent platforms in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.03,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,There's still water in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.03,0:21:27.58,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hallway connecting \Nthe annex to the main building,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:29.51,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,but it's being remodeled right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.64,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit out of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:34.23,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,but we could go outside and come\Nback in through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.81,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head there, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.91,0:21:43.79,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's the annex.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.53,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Since only our footprints \Nare here, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:52.66,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,No one has been this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:56.05,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:58.54,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.36,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Get the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:01.88,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.21,DCMain,TAKAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's not turning on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:08.83,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that sliding door?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:12.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It's broken as though \Nsomething cut through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.33,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:24:09.05,DCEpPreview,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:49.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is there blood above the cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:52.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,To make it look like the kamaitachi did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:56.16,DCMain,YAMAMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The suspect is a kamaitachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.89,0:23:58.20,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:02.95,DCMain,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,Demons don't bother with breaking \Nwindows or shutting off breakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.45,0:24:07.09,DCItalic,HEIJI,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:09.05,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:15.05,DCNextEp,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,The Kamaitachi Inn\N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.64,0:24:13.58,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Conan is \N"The Kamaitachi Inn, Part Two!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.07,0:24:35.07,Hint,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuyu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.80,0:24:32.96,DCMain,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.96,0:24:34.69,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.07,0:24:36.61,DCMain,RAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kazuha-chan, how are things with Hattori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.07,0:24:40.07,Don'tMiss,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.61,0:24:37.84,DCMain,KAZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, actually—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.84,0:24:39.89,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We're out of time. See you next week.
